---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const isHomePage = Astro.url.pathname === '/' || Astro.url.pathname === '/prueba/' || Astro.url.pathname.endsWith('/index.html');
const isDev = import.meta.env.DEV;
const basePath = isDev ? '' : '/prueba';
---

<footer class="site-footer">
	<div class="container footer-grid">
		<div class="col">
			<a class="brand" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}`} aria-label="LegalDatos">
				<img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}logo-legaldatos.png`} width="136"  alt="LegalDatos" />
			</a>
			<p class="desc" style="font-size: 16px;">
				Nuestra consultora ofrece asesorías a todo tipo de organizaciones en la adopción 
				de mejores prácticas para la protección de datos, integrando la actual normativa
				 de datos personales y compliance de datos en el núcleo de su gobernanza.
			</p>
			<a class="link" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}nosotros`}>Nosotros</a>
		</div>

		<div class="col">
			<h3 class="title">Nuestros servicios</h3>
			<a class="link" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}servicios`}>Ver servicios</a>
			<a class="link" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}contacto`}>Solicitar asesoría</a>
			<a class="link" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}publicaciones`}>Publicaciones</a>
		</div>

		<div class="col">
			<h3 class="title">Datos de contacto</h3>
			<div class="contact-item">
				<svg class="icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
					<path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path>
				</svg>
				<a class="link" href="tel:+56968434272">+56 9 6843 4272</a>
			</div>
			<div class="contact-item">
				<svg class="icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
					<path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
					<polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
				</svg>
				<a class="link" href="mailto:contacto@legaldatos.cl">contacto@legaldatos.cl</a>
			</div>
			<div class="contact-item">
				<svg class="icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
					<path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path>
					<circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
				</svg>
				<span class="link">Huérfanos 757 oficina 614, Santiago</span>
			</div>
			<h3 class="title" style="padding-top: 24px;">Redes Sociales</h3>
			<a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/legaldatoscl/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
			<a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/legaldatos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
		</div>


	</div>

	<div class="container bottom">
		<p class="copyright">@2026  LegalDatos por <a href="https://diseñopaginas.cl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">diseñopaginas.cl</a></p>
		<a class="link" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}politica-de-privacidad/`}>Política de Privacidad</a>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.site-footer {
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		background: #0C1630;
		padding-top: 64px;
		padding-bottom: 28px;
	}

	.footer-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 24px;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.brand {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 10px;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.brand-mark {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 36px;
		height: 36px;
		border-radius: 10px;
		background: var(--accent);
		color: #0C1630;
		font-size: 16px;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.brand-text {
		font-size: 16px;
	}

	.desc {
		margin: 14px 0;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
		line-height: 1.6;
		max-width: 40ch;
	}

	.title {
		margin: 0 0 12px;
		font-size: 16px;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
	}

	.col {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 10px;
	}

	.link {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 16px;
		transition: color 0.2s ease;
	}

	.link:hover {
		color: var(--accent);
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.contact-item {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 8px;
		margin-bottom: 8px;
	}

	.icon {
		color: var(--accent);
		flex-shrink: 0;
		opacity: 0.8;
		transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
	}

	.contact-item:hover .icon {
		opacity: 1;
	}

	.bottom {
		margin-top: 28px;
		padding-top: 18px;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		display: flex;
		gap: 12px;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.copyright {
		margin: 0;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
		font-size: 14px;
	}

	@media (max-width: 860px) {
		.footer-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.desc {
			max-width: none;
		}
	}
</style>
